                     <title key="work_7378">Sermones 'Filius matris'</title>
                     <incipit>Viro bone fame ... W. Dei gratia . N. ecclesie dispensatori fedelissimo, Filius matris sue ...</incipit>
                     <incipit> Quoniam nonnullos nostri temporis</incipit>
                     <incipit><quote>Appropinquans Ihesus ...</quote> Non sum magni causa misterij</incipit>
                     <note>Schneyer II.509–13 (this manuscript).</note>
                     <note>A list of the sermons is on fol. iii verso.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem class="#sermones" xml:id="MS_Bodl_303-item1a">
                     <note> At fol. 69v follows a single sermon on the Assumption</note>
                     <incipit>Astitit regina a dextris tuis. Beata Maria a dextris tuis</incipit>
                  </msItem>
